summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2012 FORD F-150 HAULING A 2016 PACIFIC COACHWORKS POWERLITE 24FBX (NA) TRAILER. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE FRONT DRIVER'S TIRE FRACTURED FROM THE TRAILER. THE TRAILER WAS SERVICED BY I-15 RV (11854 MARIPOSA RD, HESPERIA, CA 92345, (760) 947-8200). THE CONTACT WAS WAITING TO RECEIVE A RESPONSE FROM THE MANUFACTURER TO DETERMINE IF THERE WAS A WEIGHT DISTRIBUTION FAILURE DUE TO A DISCREPANCY WITH THE STICKER PERTAINING TO SUPPORTING THE WHEELS OF THE TRAILER. THE CONTACT WAS WAITING FOR A RESPONSE FROM THE MANUFACTURER FOR A SOLUTION.
